name: Lunch Rush: Overdrive (Pizza Tower but it's Generated in Gemini AI)
description:
I have decided to make Pizza Tower using Gemini AI to push it to it's limits, it has a the moveset from the game (sadly no noise moveset), collectable food, a combo-system, and a Lap 3!

AI's description:
A high-speed, momentum-based platformer where you play as Gus, a frantic delivery chef escaping a malfunctioning noodle factory. Builds speed, maintains combos, and features a high-stress escape sequence.
